numerical_variables

library(tidyverse)
library(kableExtra)
library(janitor)
natl2017_sample_4k <- readRDS("/cloud/project/data/natl2017_sample_4k.rds")

2017 USA Birth Data

Variables of Interest

variable description
mager mother’s age
wtgain mother weight gain
bmi Mother’s Body Mass Index
dbwt baby’s birthweight
combgest length of pregnancy

Numerical Summary

natl2017_sample_4k %>% 
  filter(combgest < 52) %>% 
    summarize(n = n(),
            min = min(combgest),
            q1 = quantile(combgest, probs=0.25),
            median = median(combgest),
            mean = mean(combgest),
            q3 = quantile(combgest, probs=0.75),
            max = max(combgest),
            sd = sd(combgest)) %>% 
    kable() %>% 
            kable_styling(full_width = F, position="left")
n min q1 median mean q3 max sd
3998 19 38 39 38.61906 40 47 2.430357 
hist(natl2017_sample_4k$combgest)

natl2017_sample_4k %>% 
  filter(combgest < 52) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(combgest)) +
    geom_histogram(aes(y=..density..),
                   binwidth = 1, 
                   color="white", 
                   fill="skyblue",
                   boundary=0)

natl2017_sample_4k %>% 
  filter(combgest < 52) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(combgest)) +
    geom_density(adjust=2,
                 color="white", 
                   fill="skyblue")

natl2017_sample_4k %>% 
  filter(combgest < 52) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(y=combgest, x=0)) +
    geom_violin(adjust=2,
                draw_quantiles=c(0.25,0.5,.75),
                color="steelblue",
                fill="skyblue")+
    coord_flip()

natl2017_sample_4k %>% 
  filter(combgest < 52) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(y=combgest)) +
    geom_boxplot(color="steelblue",
                fill="skyblue")+
    coord_flip()

natl2017_sample_4k %>% 
  filter(combgest < 52) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x=combgest, y=0)) +
    geom_jitter(color="skyblue",
                alpha=0.2,
                size=0.5)

natl2017_sample_4k %>% 
  filter(combgest < 52) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(y=combgest, x=0)) +
    geom_boxplot(width=0.5,
                 outlier.shape = NA)+
    geom_jitter(alpha=0.2, color="steelblue", size=0.5)+
    coord_flip()

natl2017_sample_4k %>% 
  filter(combgest < 52) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(y=combgest, x=0)) +
    geom_violin(adjust=2,
                draw_quantiles=c(0.25,0.5,.75),
                color="steelblue")+
    geom_jitter(color="steelblue",
                alpha=0.2,
                size=0.5,)+
    coord_flip()+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(20,50))

d1 <- data.frame(val=rnorm(4000,39,1.5))
ggplot(d1, aes(x=0, y=val)) +
  geom_violin(adjust=1,
                draw_quantiles=c(0.25,0.5,.75),
                color="steelblue")+
    geom_jitter(color="steelblue",
                alpha=0.2,
                size=0.5)+
  coord_flip()+
  scale_y_continuous(limits = c(20,50))

ggplot(d1, aes(x=val)) +
    geom_histogram(aes(y=..density..),
                   binwidth = 1, 
                   color="white", 
                   fill="skyblue",
                   boundary=0)+
